<center><table width=75%>
<tr><td bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>
<center><strong>Lightning Storm</strong></center>
</font></td></tr>
</table></center>
<table width=70%>
<tr><td>Mana:</td>
<td>137</td></tr>
<tr><td>Skill:</td>
<td>Evocation</td></tr>
<tr><td valign=top>
Classes:</td>
<td>
<a href="/spells/wizard.shtml">
Wizard</a>
 (24)<BR>
</td></tr>
<tr><td valign=top>Items:</td>
<td>
<a href="/weapons/2h_blunt.shtml#adamantite_bo_stick">Adamantite Bo Stick</a><br>
</td></tr>
<tr><td>Buyable:</td><td>
No</td></tr>
<tr><td>Researchable:</td><td>
Yes</td></tr>
<tr><td>Drops from MOB:</td><td>
No</td></tr>
<tr><td>Cast Time:</td>
<td>3.60 seconds</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan=2><br></td></tr>
<tr><td colspan=2>Description:</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan=2>
Deals up to 75 damage to targets within the spells area of effect.</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan=2>
<BR>1 tick = 6 seconds<BR>
When a range of effects are given, it usually means that the effect becomes more potent as the caster increases in levels.
</td></tr>
</table>
