<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I am a monk who uses the stick. You must be very careful when using it!  First stay just close enough that you hit the target, dont stand any closer then this!  If you do get hit by the first wave back up away from target, 2 and 3 wave misses.  I have read SV magic (a least 50) will prevent the user from getting hit by it, but have not been able to conform this.  Spent all my $ on buying the stick. Trying to buy some SV magic things now.  The waves have been any where from 1-3 waves.  I have had the stick proc 3 times in one fight against a forest gaint!  The gaint never even hit me!  </font></td></tr></table>
